data.meta_description:
8 likes, 1 comments - usembassynz on August 16, 2023: "Posted @withregram • @antarcticheritage Do you know someone in Year 7 – 9 who is keen to step outside their comfort zone and develop their explorer mindset on a weekend of Antarctic themed fun and learning in the Antarctic Gateway city Ōtautahi Christchurch!

Applications are now open for our next Young Inspiring Explorers™ Summit!!

In partnership with @williampikechallengeaward and supported by the @usembassynz, @internationalantarcticcentre and @antarcticanz the weekend will offer successful applicants exciting opportunities including:

❄️Meeting huskies and riding in a Hägglund at the International Antarctic Centre
❄️Camping out in a tent
❄️ Exploring Christchurch on an Antarctic scavenger hunt
❄️ Experiencing interactive Antarctic science
❄️ Making new friends

25 places are available on the Summit, which will run Friday 10 November to Sunday 12 November.
Applications close Sunday 10 September

For more information and to apply see link in bio

#inspiringexplorers #explore #inspire #discover #antarctica #youngexplorers #applynow".
